### Get tasks by project
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/1/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get tasks filtered by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/1/tasks?status=TODO
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get tasks filtered by priority
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/1/tasks?priority=MEDIUM
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get task by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/1/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create task
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/1/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Ma première tâche",
  "description": "Description de la tâche",
  "status": "TODO",
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "dueDate": "2026-12-31"
}

### Create task — validation error (blank title)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/1/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "",
  "status": "TODO",
  "priority": "MEDIUM"
}

### Update task
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/1/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Tâche modifiée",
  "description": "Description modifiée",
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS",
  "priority": "HIGH"
}

### Delete task
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/1/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Type mismatch error
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/abc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}